U7 chit8 jit8 Gui7 Lo2-ia5 ti7 hoe-hng5 teh iu5-siuN2 khoaN3-kiN3 Bi2-le7 tui3 chhiu7-kha chau2 chhut lai5 khi3 pho7 hit chiah kau2-a2 e5 am7-kun2 ka7 phah-to2 tiam3 ti7 thou5-kha. Kau2-a2 toa7-siaN hau2, chit8-e7 peh-khi2-lai5 Bi2-le7 ia7 hou7 i phah poah8-to2. Gui7 Lo2 -ia5 m7 chai sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3, chiu7-mng7 Bi2-le7,“Li2 teh cho3 sim2-mih8 mih8? Kin2-kin2 ka7 goa2 kong2 lah!”Bi2-le7 chiu7 lai5 kong2,“Goa2 beh koaiN-si2 hit-chiah kau2-a2. Ku7-ia5 li2 m7 chai i si7 sai-a2, goa2 si7 Tai7-pit8; i lai5, si7 beh chiah8 goa2 e5 iuN5, sou2-i2 goa2 beh hou7 i si2,” Gui7 Lo2 -ia5 kong2,“Li2 che si7 teh kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7?”Bi2-le7 chiu7 kong2, “Ku7-ia5 kam2 be7 ki3-tit Seng3-keng u7 kong2 Tai7-pit8 ong5 phah si2 sai-a2 kiu3 i e5 iuN5 mah? Goa2 ti7-chia teh chhit-tho5 chiu7-si7 chit e5 khoan2-sit.”
Gui7 Lo2-ia5 kong2,“Li2 m7-thang an2-ni chhit-tho5, kiaN-liau2 kau2-a2 e7 ka7-li2. Li2 iau2 u7 sim2-mih8 chhit-tho5 e5 hoat-tou7?”Bi2-le7 chiu7 kong2,“Li2 khoaN3 chit chang5-chhiu7 chin7 kou-ta5 goa2 liah8 i cho3 Kho-li7-a chiu7 eng7 chioh8-thau5 tim3 i si2, chhin-chhiuN7 Tai7-pit8 phah-si2 hit e5 toa7-han3 lang5 e5 khoan2-sit.”Gui7 Lo2-ia5 mng7 kong2,“Li2 chhit-tho5 long2 si7 hai7 si2 lang5 kap mih8 mah?”Bi2-le7 chhio3 kong2,“M7 si7 lah! Ku7-ia5 li2 khoaN3 hit chang5-chhiu7 long7-tong7-chu2 chhut-mng5 phoa3-hui3 chiN5-chai5. Chai7 goa7 bin7 siu7-khou2, chiu7-si7 na2 tiam3 chhiu7-kha sim-lai7 hoan2-hoe2-choe7 siuN7 beh hoe5-ka. Ku7-ia5, koh khoaN3 hit chang5 u7 ang5-hioh8 e5 chhiu7. Hia si7 pe7-bu2 e5 ke, goa2 chau2 kau3 hit tah kong2.‘Goa2 tek-choe7 pe7 lah; kiu5 pe7 sia3-bian2.’Goa2 chiu7 che7 tiam3 hia chiah8 piaN2 sim-lai7 chin khoai3-lok8.” Gui7 Lo2-ia5 mng7,“Li2 an2-ni teh chhit-tho5 long2 si7 tui3 Seng3-keng lai5 mah?”Bi2-le7 kong2,“Goa2 kai3 hoaN-hi2 Seng3-keng-nih8 kou3-su7, lau2-ma jit8-jit8 kong2 hou7 goa2 thiaN; goa2 sou2 ai3 chiu7-si7 long7-chu2 hoe5-thau5. Ku7-ia5 li2 kiam2 bo5 ai3 hit e5 kou3-su7 mah?” Bo2-ku7 bo5 in3 i cho3 i jip8 chhu3-lai7 khi3, sim-lai7 bo5 peng5-an, in-ui7 ka-ti7 siuN7 kui2-ni5 cheng5 i ia7 si7 hoaN-hi2 khoaN3 Seng3-keng jit8-jit8 ki5-to2. Chong2--si7 hoat-chiN5 liau2-au7 hou7 goa7-su7 kap cheng5-iok8 jia-kham3 to7-li2, chiu7 soa3 be7 kiat koe2-chi2 lah! Sui-jian5 mui2 le2-pai3 khi3 pai3-tng5 keng3 siong7-te3, ku2 ti7 chhu3-lai7 bo5 khoaN3 Seng3-keng, ia7 bo5 ki5-to2, chhin-chhiuN7 chiong Siong7-te3 pang3 be7 ki3-tit chit8-iuN7. 
Kin-a2-jit8 thiaN-kiN3 Bi2-le7 e5 oe7 sim-lai7 teh siuN7,“Goa2 na2 hit e5 long7-tong7-chu2 li7-khui ThiN-pe7.” Kau3-boe2 i iu5-goan5 m7-kheng2 jin7 choe7 lai5 kui-hok8 Siong7-te3; sou2 i2 sim-lai7 iau2-boe7 an-jian5. Bi2-le7 m7 chai Ku7-ia5 si7 an2-ni; ia7 m7 si7 tiau5-kou3-i3 kong2-chhut hia e5 oe7. Na7-si7 Siong7-te3 eng7 chit e5 gin2-a2 e5 oe7 hou7 Gui7 Lo2-ia5 e5 sim ban7-ban7 chheN2-gou7. Bi2-le7 lai5 e5 si5 i e5 bo2-ku7 bo5 sim2-mih8 hoaN-hi2, chong2--si7 chiam7-chiam7 pian3-oaN7 sim-lai7 na2 gau5 thiaN3 i; sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni u7 chit8 jit8 siu7-khi3 me7 i. Chit-e5 si7 ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 leh? Si7 ui7-tioh8 Bi2-le7 chhoa7 kau2-a2 khi3 chhu3-lai7 chhit-tho5. Hit-si5 teh phah-kiu5 hou7 kau2-a2 lai5 jek. Kau2-a2 teh jek kiu5 khap-tioh8 toh-kui7 chiu7 chiong kek8 kou2-cha2, kek8 kui3-khi3 e5 hoe-kan, chhia-to2 thou5-kha phah-phoa3.
